(36, 1, '2018-09-16 17:12:23', '2018-09-16 17:12:23', '<h2><strong>Hi Guys!!! I have a wonderful low carbs, Keto friendly chocolate chip cookies recipe for you.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2><img class="alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-343" src="http://maxinescorner.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/IMG_9981-150x150.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="150" /></h2>\r\nIf you have been searching a perfect recipe look no further, you can thank me later. Let start making these wonderful low carbs cookies. You can’t go wrong combining chocolate chips and oatmeal.\r\n<h5>Ingredients</h5>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>2 cups of oat flour</li>\r\n 	<li>1/3 cups brown sugar</li>\r\n 	<li>1/2 Teaspoon Baking powder</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<strong>Wet Ingredients</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>1/2 Vegan Butter melted</li>\r\n 	<li>1 teaspoon vanilla extract</li>\r\n 	<li>2 large eggs</li>\r\n 	<li>2/3 cups chocolate chips (semi-sweet)</li>\r\n 	<li>Refrigerate for 2 hours.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bake at 350 Degrees for 10 Minutes</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<strong>Instructions</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Preheat oven 350 degrees, line baking sheet with nonstick sheet or parchment paper.</li>\r\n 	<li>In a bowl large mixing bowl, mix together oat flour, brown sugar and making powder (make sure there is no lumps in the sugar).</li>\r\n 	<li>Mix in the eggs, vanilla extract and melted butter until thoroughly combined.</li>\r\n 	<li>Take the bowl with the oat flour mixture and add the wet ingredients to it. Mix thoroughly.</li>\r\n 	<li>Stir in the chocolate chips to combine.</li>\r\n 	<li>Using a cookie scoop or spoon, place cookie dough balls on cookie mat or parchment paper</li>\r\n 	<li>Place dough in refrigerator for 2 hours or freezer for 15 to 20 minutes</li>\r\n 	<li>Remove from refrigerator or freezer.</li>\r\n 	<li>bake for 10 minutes</li>\r\n 	<li>Remove from oven and transfer to parchment paper or non stick mat and place on cooling rack.</li>\r\n 	<li>Allow to cool for 10 minutes. Store in airtight container or plastic bags.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Watch the video subscribe to the channel for more healthy tips</strong>\r\n<iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/K6o4axdfJFs?rel=0" width="560" height="315" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" data-mce-fragment="1"></iframe>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Perfect Chocolate Chips Cookies', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'perfect-chocolate-chips-cookies', '', '', '2018-09-16 18:04:55', '2018-09-16 18:04:55', '', 0, 'http://localhost/MaxinesCorner/?p=36', 0, 'post', '', 0),
